de.ovgu.featureide.fm.attributes.base.impl

Class FeatureAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ovgu.featureide.fm.attributes.base.impl.FeatureAttribute
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFeatureAttribute
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanFeatureAttribute, DoubleFeatureAttribute, LongFeatureAttribute, StringFeatureAttribute

    public abstract class FeatureAttribute
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFeatureAttribute
    Abstract class subclassed by every type of feature attribute. Provides many function used by all types of attributes.
    Author:
    Joshua Sprey, Chico Sundermann
